#slide1.row.reset-layout
  .col-md-7.centered-text
    %h1.text-white
      Improve the lives of
      %br.hidden-xs
      people with sleep apnea
    %h3.text-light8
      Awareness, community, research -
      %br
      together, we're building it all.
  #signup-form-above-fold.col-md-4
    %p.f500.centered
      It's within your power to have an impact on the future of sleep apnea - connect with other people, doctors, and researchers and let your voice be heard!
    - resource = User.new
    = form_for(resource, url: registration_path(resource), method: :post) do |f|
      .input-group
        .col-sm-6
          = f.text_field :first_name, placeholder: 'First name', class: "form-control"
        .col-sm-6
          = f.text_field :last_name, placeholder: 'Last name', class: "form-control"
      .input-group
        .col-sm-12
          = f.email_field :email, placeholder: 'Email address', class: "form-control"
      .input-group
        .col-sm-12
          = f.password_field :password, placeholder: 'Password', class: "form-control"
      .input-group.centered
        = f.submit 'Join Today', id: "btn-join"

  #scroll-carat.hidden-sm.hidden-xs
    %p.text-light7
      Scroll to Learn More
    %h4.text-light7
      %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-down

#slide2
  .text-content-container
    %h2#myapnea-mission.f300.text-white
      Our mission is to improve the diagnosis and treatment of sleep apnea through the
      %span.lighter-orange active engagement
      of patients, families, researchers, and healthcare providers.
    %br
    .row
      .col-sm-offset-1.col-sm-4.col-sm-push-7
        = image_tag 'myapnea/icons/data_powerful.png', class: 'img-responsive', style: 'max-width:150px;'
      .col-sm-7.col-sm-pull-4
        %h3.text-white Your Data is Powerful
        %p.text-light8
          Research relies on people like you to help by sharing important data to find the best outcomes.
        = link_to 'Participate in Research', get_tracked_link(:surveys), class: 'btn btn-warning'
    %br
    %br
    .row
      .col-sm-offset-1.col-sm-4.col-sm-push-7
        = image_tag 'myapnea/icons/risk2.png', class: 'img-responsive', style: 'max-width:150px;'
      .col-sm-7.col-sm-pull-4
        %h3.text-white Are You at Risk?
        %p.text-light8
          Over 80% of sleep apnea cases go undiagnosed. Take our quick test and see if you're at risk.
        = link_to 'Check Your Risk', get_tracked_link(:check_risk), class: 'btn btn-warning'
    %br
    %br
    .row
      .col-sm-offset-1.col-sm-4.col-sm-push-7
        = image_tag 'myapnea/icons/speech_bubbles.png', class: 'img-responsive', style: 'max-width:150px; '
      .col-sm-7.col-sm-pull-4
        %h3.text-white Welcome to Our Community
        %p.text-light8
          Families, researchers, and care providers have all come together to help each other in amazing ways.
        = link_to 'See the Community', get_tracked_link(:forums), class: 'btn btn-warning'

#slide3
  #testimonial-giver
    = image_tag 'myapnea/testimonials/KathyPage.jpg', class: 'img-responsive'
  #testimonial
    %p.lead
      "It seems as if research is generally driven by funding organizations, which oftentimes is not reflective of the needs of patients. By having large amounts of data provided by and for us, we can now drive the research agenda. This is a way to democratize researchâ€”to generate understanding on the part of the researchers and patients together."
    %h4.centered
      \- Kathy Page
      %span.f300 (Missouri, USA)
  .clearfix

#slide4
  .text-content-container
    %h1.text-white.centered
      In ten minutes, you can:
    %br
    .row
      .col-md-4
        .circle
          %span Join an awesome, international research project
      .col-md-4
        .circle
          %span Shape research to better benefit people like you
      .col-md-4
        .circle
          %span Connect with thousands of supportive people

    #slide-money
      %h2.text-white
        Plus, earn rewards for your help!
      %h3.f300.text-light8
        For every survey that you complete, you'll be entered into a
        %br
        monthly drawing for a
        %span.f500.text-white $250 Visa gift card.


#slide5
  .text-content-container.centered
    %h1.text-white
      %span.primary-orange= number_with_delimiter User.current.count
      people are already making a difference
    = link_to 'Join Today', get_tracked_link(:join_from_landing), class: 'btn btn-primary', id: 'btn-join'

